2 \u0915\u093f\u090f \u0917\u090f \u0906\u0924\u094d\u092e\u0928\u093f\u0930\u094d\u092d\u0930 \u092d\u093e\u0930\u0924 \u0905\u092d\u093f\u092f\u093e\u0928 \u0915\u0940 \u0938\u092e\u094d\u092a\u0942\u0930\u094d\u0923 \u091c\u093e\u0928\u0915\u093e\u0930\u0940 \u091c\u093f\u0938\u0915\u0947 \u0924\u0939\u0924 \u0926\u0947\u0936 \u092d\u0930 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0935\u093f\u092d\u093f\u0928\u094d\u0928 \u0915\u094d\u0937\u0947\u0924\u094d\u0930\u094b\u0902 \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f 20 \u0932\u093e\u0916 \u0915\u0930\u094b\u095c \u0930\u0941\u092a\u090f \u0915\u0947 \u0906\u0930\u094d\u0925\u093f\u0915 \u092a\u0948\u0915\u0947\u091c \u0915\u0940 \u0918\u094b\u0937\u0923\u093e \u0915\u0940 \u0917\u0908 \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u091c\u093e\u0928\u093f\u090f \u0906\u0924\u094d\u092e\u0928\u093f\u0930\u094d\u092d\u0930 \u092d\u093e\u0930\u0924 \u0905\u092d\u093f\u092f\u093e\u0928 \u0915\u0947 \u0924\u0939\u0924 \u0939\u0941\u092f\u0940 \u092e\u0941\u0916\u094d\u092f \u0918\u094b\u0937\u0923\u093e\u0913\u0902 \u0915\u0947 \u092c\u093e\u0930\u0947 \u092e\u0947\u0902</div> <!-- post thumbnail --><div class=\"fpostimage\"> <img src=\"https://sarkariyojana.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/atmanirbhar-bharat-abhiyan-apply-online-form.jpg\" alt=\"Atmanirbhar Bharat Abhiyan Apply Online Form\"/></div><div class=\"hbidad\"><center><div id=\"div-gpt-ad-ATD-SY-P3\"></div></center></div><div class=\"entry-content\" id=\"cprint\"><p><strong>Atmanirbhar Bharat Abhiyan 2020:</strong> PM Narendra Modi in his address to the nation on 12 May 2020 has announced a new <strong>Atmanirbhar Bharat Abhiyan</strong> 2020. In this Self Reliant India Campaign, the <a href=\"https://sarkariyojana.com/central-government/\">central govt.</a> will lay special emphasis on economy growth, local production of goods, strengthening supply chain and raising demand of products. To make India a self reliant (\u0906\u0924\u094d\u092e\u0928\u093f\u0930\u094d\u092d\u0930) country, central govt. has announced an economic package of Rs. 20 lakh crore. People can now check list of schemes for MSMEs, Education, Health, Agriculture &#038; other sectors.</p><div class=\"googleads mobad\"> <!-- SYRLU2 --> <ins class=\"adsbygoogle mobad\" style=\"display:block\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-9413286941447335\" data-ad-slot=\"4369456947\" data-ad-format=\"link\"></ins> <script>(adsbygoogle=window.adsbygoogle||[]).push({});</script> </div><p>In his speech, Prime Minister Modi said that the central govt. will provide 20 lakh crore in 2020 (20 Lakh Crore in 20-20). This Atmanirbhar Bharat Abhiyan package is inclusive of the already announced <a href=\"https://sarkariyojana.com/pm-garib-kalyan-yojana/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">1.7 lakh crore PM Garib Kalyan Yojana</a> and <a href=\"https://sarkariyojana.com/rbi-coronavirus-live-news-update/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">1.7 lakh crore package by the RBI</a>. The main focus of Atmanirbhar Bharat Abhiyan will be on making India a manufacturing hub as the country has youngest workforce.</p><p>This <a href=\"https://sarkariyojana.com/aatmanirbhar-bharat-abhiyan/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Aatmanirbhar Bharat Abhiyan 2020</a> package is approx. 10% of the total Gross Domestic Product (GDP) of India. Now we are going to provide you the details of the self reliant India campaign such as 4 L&#8217;s factors, beneficiaries, sectors to benefit etc.</p><div class=\"googleads\"> <!-- SYRLU2 --> <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:block\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-9413286941447335\" data-ad-slot=\"4369456947\" data-ad-format=\"link\"></ins> <script>(adsbygoogle=window.adsbygoogle||[]).push({});</script> </div><div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_11 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal\"><div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\"><p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Table of Contents</p> <span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-